---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import { getArticles } from "../lib/articles";

const articles = await getArticles();
const articleCount = articles.length;
---

<Base title="AI — islam.se" description="Anslut din AI-assistent till islam.se och sök bland alla essäer direkt i samtalet.">
	<main id="main" class="content-column">
		<header class="article-header">
			<h1>AI</h1>
		</header>

		<div class="article-body prose ai-prose">
			<p>Samtliga {articleCount} essäer finns tillgängliga via en öppen <a href="https://modelcontextprotocol.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MCP-server</a> &ndash; ett protokoll som låter AI-assistenter använda externa verktyg. Claude, ChatGPT och andra assistenter kan söka i, läsa och citera essäerna direkt i samtalet.</p>

			<div class="tool-list">
				<dl>
					<div class="tool-item">
						<dt><code>search_articles</code></dt>
						<dd>Fritextsökning bland alla essäer</dd>
					</div>
					<div class="tool-item">
						<dt><code>get_article</code></dt>
						<dd>Hämtar en hel essä med metadata</dd>
					</div>
					<div class="tool-item">
						<dt><code>list_articles</code></dt>
						<dd>Listar alla publicerade essäer</dd>
					</div>
				</dl>
			</div>

			<div class="server-url" data-url="https://mcp.islam.se/mcp">
				<span class="server-url-label">Serveradress</span>
				<code class="server-url-value">https://mcp.islam.se/mcp</code>
				<button class="copy-btn" type="button" aria-label="Kopiera serveradress">
					<svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
						<rect x="5.5" y="5.5" width="8" height="8" rx="1.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.25" />
						<path d="M10.5 5.5V3.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-1.5-1.5H3.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 2 3.5V9a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5 1.5h2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.25" />
					</svg>
					<span class="copy-label">Kopiera</span>
				</button>
			</div>

			<div class="section-ornament"></div>

			<h2>Claude Desktop</h2>
			<ol>
				<li>Öppna <strong>Settings</strong> (<kbd>Cmd</kbd><kbd>,</kbd> eller <kbd>Ctrl</kbd><kbd>,</kbd>).</li>
				<li>Gå till <strong>Developer</strong> &rarr; <strong>Edit Config</strong>.</li>
				<li>Lägg till:</li>
			</ol>
			<div class="code-block">
				<pre><code>{`{
  "mcpServers": {
    "islam-se": {
      "url": "https://mcp.islam.se/mcp"
    }
  }
}`}</code></pre>
				<button class="copy-code" type="button" aria-label="Kopiera kod">
					<svg class="copy-icon" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
						<rect x="5.5" y="5.5" width="8" height="8" rx="1.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.25" />
						<path d="M10.5 5.5V3.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-1.5-1.5H3.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 2 3.5V9a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5 1.5h2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.25" />
					</svg>
					<svg class="check-icon" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true" style="display:none">
						<path d="M3 8.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
					</svg>
				</button>
			</div>
			<ol start="4">
				<li>Spara och starta om Claude.</li>
			</ol>

			<h2>Claude.ai</h2>
			<ol>
				<li>Logga in på <a href="https://claude.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">claude.ai</a>.</li>
				<li>Gå till <strong>Settings</strong> &rarr; <strong>Integrations</strong> &rarr; <strong>Add&nbsp;integration</strong>.</li>
				<li>Klistra in serveradressen.</li>
			</ol>

			<h2>ChatGPT</h2>
			<ol>
				<li>Gå till <strong>Settings</strong> &rarr; <strong>Tools</strong> &rarr; <strong>Add MCP server</strong>.</li>
				<li>Klistra in serveradressen.</li>
			</ol>

			<h2>Claude Code</h2>
			<div class="code-block">
				<pre><code>claude mcp add -s user --transport http islam-se https://mcp.islam.se/mcp</code></pre>
				<button class="copy-code" type="button" aria-label="Kopiera kommando">
					<svg class="copy-icon" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
						<rect x="5.5" y="5.5" width="8" height="8" rx="1.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.25" />
						<path d="M10.5 5.5V3.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-1.5-1.5H3.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 2 3.5V9a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5 1.5h2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.25" />
					</svg>
					<svg class="check-icon" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true" style="display:none">
						<path d="M3 8.5l3.5 3.5 6.5-7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
					</svg>
				</button>
			</div>

			<div class="section-ornament"></div>

			<h2>Prova</h2>
			<p>När servern är kopplad, skriv till exempel:</p>
			<blockquote>
				<p>Sök bland essäerna på islam.se efter texter om Strindberg och islam.</p>
			</blockquote>
			<p>Assistenten söker, hittar relevanta essäer och kan citera dem med länk tillbaka till islam.se.</p>
		</div>
	</main>
</Base>

<style>
	/* Disable book-style paragraph indentation — this is technical prose */
	.ai-prose > :global(p + p:not([class])) {
		text-indent: 0;
	}

	.ai-prose > :global(p:has(+ p)) {
		margin-bottom: var(--space-unit);
	}

	/* Tool list — definition list */
	.tool-list {
		margin-block: var(--space-unit);
	}

	.tool-list dl {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
	}

	.tool-item {
		display: flex;
		align-items: baseline;
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.tool-item dt {
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.tool-item dd {
		color: var(--color-muted);
		font-size: 0.9375em;
	}

	@media (width <= 480px) {
		.tool-item {
			flex-direction: column;
			gap: 0.125rem;
		}
	}

	/* Code — monospace for tool names and config blocks */
	.ai-prose :global(code) {
		font-family: ui-monospace, "SF Mono", "Cascadia Code", "Segoe UI Mono", Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
		font-size: 0.85em;
		font-variant-numeric: lining-nums tabular-nums;
		letter-spacing: 0;
	}

	.ai-prose :global(pre) {
		background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-bg), var(--color-muted) 4%);
		border: 1px solid var(--color-divider);
		border-radius: 0.375rem;
		padding: 0.875rem 1.25rem;
		font-size: 0.8125rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		overflow-x: auto;
		-webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
	}

	@media (width <= 480px) {
		.ai-prose :global(pre) {
			padding: 0.75rem 0.875rem;
			font-size: 0.75rem;
			border-radius: 0.25rem;
		}
	}

	/* Code block with copy button */
	.code-block {
		position: relative;
	}

	.copy-code {
		position: absolute;
		top: 0.5rem;
		right: 0.5rem;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		width: 2rem;
		height: 2rem;
		padding: 0;
		color: var(--color-muted);
		background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-bg), var(--color-muted) 8%);
		border: 1px solid var(--color-divider);
		border-radius: 0.25rem;
		cursor: pointer;
		opacity: 0;
		transition: opacity 0.15s, color 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;

		&:hover {
			color: var(--color-accent);
			border-color: var(--color-warm);
		}
	}

	.code-block:hover .copy-code {
		opacity: 1;
	}

	/* On touch devices, always show */
	@media (hover: none) {
		.copy-code {
			opacity: 1;
		}
	}

	/* Server URL card */
	.server-url {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		align-items: baseline;
		gap: 0.375rem;
		margin-block: var(--space-unit);
		padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
		border: 1px solid var(--color-divider);
		border-radius: 0.375rem;
		background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-bg), var(--color-muted) 4%);
	}

	.server-url-label {
		width: 100%;
		font-family: var(--font-heading);
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: var(--color-muted);
	}

	.server-url-value {
		flex: 1;
		font-size: 0.9375rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.01em;
		color: var(--color-accent);
		word-break: break-all;
	}

	@media (width <= 480px) {
		.server-url {
			padding: 0.875rem 1rem;
		}

		.server-url-value {
			font-size: 0.8125rem;
			width: 100%;
			flex: none;
		}
	}

	.copy-btn {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.35em;
		padding: 0.3rem 0.7rem;
		font-family: var(--font-heading);
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		letter-spacing: 0.06em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: var(--color-muted);
		background: none;
		border: 1px solid var(--color-divider);
		border-radius: 1rem;
		cursor: pointer;
		transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;

		&:hover {
			border-color: var(--color-warm);
			color: var(--color-accent);
		}
	}

	/* Keyboard shortcut keys */
	.ai-prose :global(kbd) {
		display: inline-block;
		min-width: 1.4em;
		padding: 0.1em 0.35em;
		font-family: ui-monospace, "SF Mono", Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
		font-size: 0.8em;
		line-height: 1.3;
		text-align: center;
		border: 1px solid var(--color-divider);
		border-radius: 0.25rem;
		background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-bg), var(--color-muted) 6%);
		box-shadow: 0 1px 0 color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-muted), transparent 75%);
	}

	.ai-prose :global(kbd + kbd) {
		margin-left: 0.15em;
	}

	/* Ordered list refinements */
	.ai-prose :global(ol) {
		padding-left: 1.25em;
	}

	.ai-prose :global(li) {
		margin-bottom: 0.35em;
	}

	/* Remove external arrow from code-only links */
	.ai-prose :global(a:has(> code)::after) {
		content: none;
	}
</style>

<script>
	document.addEventListener("astro:page-load", () => {
		// Server URL copy button
		const urlBtn = document.querySelector<HTMLButtonElement>(".copy-btn");
		const card = urlBtn?.closest<HTMLElement>(".server-url");
		if (urlBtn && card) {
			const url = card.dataset.url || "";
			const label = urlBtn.querySelector<HTMLElement>(".copy-label");
			if (label) {
				urlBtn.addEventListener("click", async () => {
					try {
						await navigator.clipboard.writeText(url);
						label.textContent = "Kopierad";
						setTimeout(() => { label.textContent = "Kopiera"; }, 2000);
					} catch {}
				});
			}
		}

		// Code block copy buttons
		for (const btn of document.querySelectorAll<HTMLButtonElement>(".copy-code")) {
			btn.addEventListener("click", async () => {
				const pre = btn.closest(".code-block")?.querySelector("code");
				if (!pre) return;
				try {
					await navigator.clipboard.writeText(pre.textContent || "");
					const copyIcon = btn.querySelector<SVGElement>(".copy-icon");
					const checkIcon = btn.querySelector<SVGElement>(".check-icon");
					if (copyIcon && checkIcon) {
						copyIcon.style.display = "none";
						checkIcon.style.display = "";
						setTimeout(() => {
							copyIcon.style.display = "";
							checkIcon.style.display = "none";
						}, 2000);
					}
				} catch {}
			});
		}
	});
</script>
